parameter 27: The episode "Too Many Girls" (aka "Davy and Fern") was originally censored (By NBC's Standards and Practices Dept.) showing a blurred lens-view of the scene where Fern is wearing a bikini. parameter 28: The scene in which Fern wins over Davy by posing as a contestant in the National Beauty Pageant (wearing a leopard skin bikini) was heavily censored on most broadcasts and even on the DVD version. All wide shots were deleted, the two-shots were cropped and the bottom right of the screen was blurred to obscure 'Kelly Jean Peters' (qv) cleavage. However, the original version has survived and is still occasionally screened.
